<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="moving-adj">moving <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'muːvɪŋ/    美 /'muːvɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>感人的；令人感动的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His letter was deeply moving. 
他的信非常感人。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>moving speech</strong> 
感人的演说</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>动的；运转中的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Reading in a moving car is harmful to your eyes. 
在行驶的车上阅读对眼睛有害。</p></div></div>